<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>   Face it, no ability this unbalancing will ever be allowed to stay in the game forever. It destroys the lower level dragon and epic mob encounters, and really breaks the entire epic process for many guilds. It can't be allowed to remain as it is. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
